plot: A country like no other in Europe, Hungary is influenced by the rhythms of its rivers. White-tailed eagles, otters and enormous catfish share the wetlands with many other species living close to the local people, often unnoticed. "Wild Hungary" is their story presenting quite a few never-before-filmed animal behaviors. Written by Zoltán Török
title: Vad Magyarország - A vizek birodalma
